{"tid":686181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[唔捱得]50後廢老 結婚一年 感情問題墮樓亡！","createTime":"2018-06-01T04:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T05:40:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50d377a97349903d29be6d1220b5ceabc3380b22","tid":686181,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】大圍昨晚發生傷人及自殺案，一名男子懷疑向妻子淋腐蝕液體後，被發現從高處墮樓不治。<br />\n<br />\n現場是隆亨邨學心樓十一樓一個單位，星期四夜晚9時許，警方接報指鄰居女戶主面及頭部受傷，警方到場後發現一名男子從高處墮樓，倒臥在一樓平台，兩名傷者被送往威爾斯醫院，其中<span style=\"color: red;\">67歲男子證實不治</span>，女傷者嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示<span style=\"color: red;\">兩人一年前結婚</span>，搬入案發單位約一年，男死者生前任職冷氣技工。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，他曾經在2010年六月在沙田排頭村與前妻發生爭執，女事主被淋腐蝕液體，嚴重受傷，留醫一個月不治，疑兇其後被裁定誤殺罪成立，2015年出獄。<br />\n<br />\n據初步調查指，今次事件<span style=\"color: red;\">相信感情問題引起</span>，警方在單位內檢走一批證物，包括兩支通渠水膠樽和一對男裝拖鞋。<br />\n<br />\n警方已列作傷人及自殺案，由沙田警區案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307811&d=FUGOQ%2FT1HVqIz2lEyQbz9f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=47562436\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307811&h=57a9a47d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307811</a>"},{"pid":"ea242c65bdf1b874c1bda1c0451daa20284a15e3","tid":686181,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437da3576ff5b0ea862d402d7ede6b569e6deac9","tid":686181,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T04:34:09.000Z","msg":"真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e632fa225e84ba258e1b8eb86fc954f632f6fbfd","tid":686181,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"有咁嘅前科嘅人都有女人痴埋去<br />\n殺咗人判咁短預咗冇阻嚇性啦<br />\n出返嚟咪又重犯"},{"pid":"e91aa58b6cc7dd6c06631cc46e8a8273fa39455e","tid":686181,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c1c78c7fbc487b9d161143e7e534d1a6bd4c6f","tid":686181,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e632fa225e84ba258e1b8eb86fc954f632f6fbfd","tid":686181,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"有咁嘅前科嘅人都有女人痴埋去<br />\n殺咗人判咁短預咗冇阻嚇性啦<br />\n出返嚟咪又重犯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:40:41.000Z","msg":"個大陸女人痴去個67歲窮港伯, 只係為左身份證姐"}]}